<h3>Synonyms</h3>
<ul>
 <li>@overview</li>
 <li>@fileoverview</li>
</ul>

<h3>Overview</h3>

<p>The @file tag provides a description for a file. Use the tag in a JSDoc comment at the beginning
of the file.
</p>

<h3>Example</h3>


{{#example}}File description
/**
 * @file Manages the configuration settings for the widget.
 * @author Rowina Sanela <rsanela@example.com>
 */
{{/example}}

